      </a>
      :
      <b>
       mnmlsm, th qck mthd
      </b>
     </h2>
     <div class="entry">
      <p>
       Sm f y mght hv, s n f yr gls, th dsr t bcm  mnmlst. Sm f y mght hv vn bght my bk,
       <a href="http://zenhabits.net/2009/09/my-new-ebook-the-simple-guide-to-a-minimalist-life/">
        Th Smpl Gd t  Mnmlst Lf
       </a>
       (nd f y dd, thnk y!).
      </p>
      <p>
       Bt th pth t bcmng  mnmlst dsn’t hv t b lng nd rds. It’s frly smpl, ctlly.
      </p>
      <p>
       Y jst d nd by lss.
      </p>
      <p>
       It’s  swtch tht y cn flp, n n nstnt: n mmnt y’r  rsrc-hggng, plltng, cnsmrst mtrlst cptlst swn (n ffns), nd th nxt, y’r  mnmlst.
      </p>
      <p>
       It jst tks th dcsn t lv wth lss, nd t b cntnt wth whr y r nd wht y hv nd wh y r.
      </p>
      <p>
       Y cn d ths, rght nw.
       <span id="more-396">
       </span>
      </p>
      <p>
       Wll ll th stff n yr lf nstntly dsppr? N, f crs nt – y’ll stll nd t chck ll yr stff. Y’ll nd t gt t f ll yr cmmtmnts, nd strt smplfyng yr schdl nd t-d lst.
      </p>
      <p>
       Tht’ll ll tk tm nd ffrt, I cncd. And thr’s mr, tht’ll tk tm: chngng yr byng hbts, chngng yr mplss, grdlly lttng g f ttchmnts, gttng sd t hvng lss.
      </p>
      <p>
       Bt tht ll cms ltr. Tht cms wth th trrtry.
      </p>
      <p>
       Fr nw, y cn jst flp th swtch: strt byng lss (rght nw), strt dng lss (rght nw), slw dwn, nd fnd cntntmnt. Rght nw, rght hr. B hppy wth wht y hv, wth yr lf, wth whr y r. Stp fcsng n wht y dn’t hv, bcs gdblsst, y hv wy mr thn mst f th wrld — vn f y gv p yr bg cr, bg hm, tns f fd, nd mst f yr pssssns. Y hv th wrld, nd y nd t lrn t lv t.
      </p>
      <p>
       It tks n nstnt. It’s hrdr thn hll, bt t cn hppn rght nw.
      </p>
